OL,3,CEl Nino officially declared but what
OL,4,Cdoes it mean for UK weather?
OL,6,FIt is likely to be a major factor in
OL,7,Fextreme and deadly weather across the
OL,8,Fplanet for the next year or so, and it
OL,9,Fmakes it incredibly likely that 2027
OL,10,Fwill set a record for the hottest year
OL,11,Fglobally.
OL,13,FIt seriously impacts the weather in
OL,14,FSouth America and Australia - but what
OL,15,Fdoes this year's strong El Nino mean
OL,16,Ffor us?
OL,18,FDoes a super El Nino impact the UK
OL,19,Fweather?
OL,26,@kD@FTwwD@^TwzD@STw
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
