OL,3,CEl Nino officially declared but what
OL,4,Cdoes it mean for UK weather?
OL,6,FStudies have found that a strong El
OL,7,FNino can increase the chance of a
OL,8,Fmilder winter in Northern Europe.
OL,10,FBut the relationship between El Nino
OL,11,Fand UK weather is much weaker than in
OL,12,Fmany other parts of the world because
OL,13,Fit happens so far away.
OL,15,FThere are three main ways it can
OL,16,Fimpact our weather patterns:
OL,18,FThese impacts are more likely to
OL,19,Fhappen during the winter in the UK.
OL,26,@kD@FTwoD@CTwrD@cTw
