OL,3,CEl Nino officially declared but what
OL,4,Cdoes it mean for UK weather?
OL,6,FBut these themes are all dependent on
OL,7,Fother climate patterns and are weak
OL,8,Fcompared to other factors which
OL,9,Finfluence our weather.
OL,11,FIt's known that any two super El Nino
OL,12,Fevents can produce quite different UK
OL,13,Fwinters.
OL,15,FWhy does El Nino have a weaker effect
OL,16,Fon the UK?
OL,18,FIn simple terms, El Nino is more
OL,19,FPacific-based, and we're in the
OL,20,FAtlantic.
