OL,3,CEl Nino officially declared but what
OL,4,Cdoes it mean for UK weather?
OL,6,FEl Nino is a warming of the tropical
OL,7,FPacific Ocean.
OL,9,FThat means countries bordering the
OL,10,FPacific - such as South America,
OL,11,FAustralia, Indonesia and western US -
OL,12,Fare close enough to be affected
OL,13,Fdirectly.
OL,15,FThey'll experience changing weather
OL,16,Fpatterns such as shifts in rainfall,
OL,17,Fdrought and temperature.
OL,26,@kD@FTwnD@FTw
