PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1781308974
OL,3,CEl Nino officially declared but what
OL,4,Cdoes it mean for UK weather?
OL,6,FIt's not that a super El Nino does not
OL,7,Faffect the UK entirely, but any
OL,8,Finfluence it may have will be indirect
OL,9,Fand weaker.
OL,11,FThe main drivers of UK weather are
OL,12,Fmuch stronger, and El Nino can easily
OL,13,Fbe over-ridden by dominating Atlantic
OL,14,Fweather patterns.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
